## üîÇ LOOPS

### FOR basics

```bat
FOR %%X IN (*.txt) DO ECHO %%X           :: Loop files
FOR %%X IN (1 2 3 4 5) DO ECHO %%X       :: Manual list
FOR /L %%X IN (1,1,5) DO ECHO %%X        :: 1 to 5 loop
FOR /R %%F IN (*.jpg) DO ECHO %%F        :: Recursive loop
FOR /D %%X IN (*) DO ECHO %%X            :: Folders only
```

### FOR with commands

```bat
FOR /F "tokens=1,2 delims=," %%A IN (file.csv) DO (
  ECHO First: %%A
  ECHO Second: %%B
)
```

