## üß† TIPS & TRICKS

* `%~n0` ‚Üí script name without extension
* `%~dp0` ‚Üí script directory
* `%~f1` ‚Üí full path of argument 1
* `PUSHD` / `POPD` ‚Üí temporary change directory stack
* `CHOICE` ‚Üí menu-style input
* `TIMEOUT /T 5` ‚Üí wait 5 seconds
* `TITLE` ‚Üí change window title
* `COLOR 0A` ‚Üí green text on black
* `START` ‚Üí open file, folder, or run command in new window

